Package eu.advance.logistics.flow.engine.api.ds

Contains the ADVANCE datastore API record classes and interfaces.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
AdvanceDataStore Interface for performing datastore related operations.
AdvanceDataStoreUpdate Interface having only the updateXYZ methods of the datastore.
 

Class Summary
AdvanceCreateModifyInfo The creation/modification time and user information.
AdvanceEmailBox Represents the connection information to a POP3(s)/IMAP(s) based email-box to retrieve messages.
AdvanceFTPDataSource The FTP data source record.
AdvanceGenerateKey Request to generate a new key.
AdvanceJDBCDataSource Description of JDBC data store records.
AdvanceJMSEndpoint Definition of a Java Messaging Service endpoint.
AdvanceKeyEntry Properties of a concrete key in a key store.
AdvanceKeyStore A record representing information about local or remote key stores.
AdvanceKeyStoreExport Request for exporting a certificate from a keystore.
AdvanceLocalFileDataSource A local file or directory data source.
AdvancePools A common pool for various communication pools.
AdvancePortSpecification Describes an input or output port of a running realm.
AdvanceRealm The status information about a realm.
AdvanceSchemaRegistryEntry The schema registry used to ask the engine about known schemas.
AdvanceSOAPChannel Describes a SOAP communication channel.
AdvanceUser User settings.
AdvanceWebDataSource The web data source configuration record.
 

Enum Summary
AdvanceEmailReceiveProtocols The enumeration of email box protocols.
AdvanceEmailSendProtocols The enumeration for protocols of sending email.
AdvanceFTPProtocols The file transfer protocols supported by ADVANCE.
AdvanceJDBCDrivers Enumeration for JDBC drivers.
AdvanceJMSDrivers Contains some predefined constants for JMS drivers.
AdvanceKeyType The key type within the keystore.
AdvanceLoginType The login types enumeration.
AdvanceNotificationGroupType The notification group types.
AdvanceRealmStatus The status enumeration of the ADVANCE Flow Engine Realm.
AdvanceUserRealmRights The allowed realm rights for an user.
AdvanceUserRights Enumeration for defining user rights.
